title: 797. DJ's Top 50 Prospects 3.0
itunes:title: 797. DJ's Top 50 Prospects 3.0
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the altercation involving Will Smith and Chris Rock at the Oscars. Then for the rest of the episode, DJ goes through his latest top 50 prospects list and the pair further break down their skill sets.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
